lead_paragraph: China's Lin Yue and Chen Aisen won gold in men’s 10 meter synchronized diving at the Rio Games on Monday, keeping alive the country's goal of a clean sweep in all eight events.

headline.print_headline: China Wins Gold in Men's 10 Meter Synchronized Diving
